CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 21, 1955, pg. 7, reads: "Gay Ninettes Party, Show-The Gay Ninettes Club...held a cocktail party and fashion show at the Greene Hearth last Sunday...Models who appeared are, left to right, top row Doris Griffin, Luela Perkins, Mary Ann Woods, Mary Jean Shipmon, Lois Watson, Lorraine Wets. Bottom row: Wilma Griffin, Doris Griffin, Linda Lewis and Dolores Lynch.-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Doris Griffin, Luela Perkins, Mary Ann Woods, Mary Jean Shipmon, Lois Weaver Watson, Lorraine Wets, and Wilma Griffin, Doris Griffin, Linda Lewis and Dolores Lynch in front, in Greene Hearth for Gay Ninettes Club fashion show
